Refrigerator - Spray SWIPE Multi-Purpose Cleaner onto the surface and wipe with SWIPE Microfiber Kitchen Towel. Interior fittings and door seal would become sparkling clean. Hob Stains - Spray SWIPE Multi-Purpose Cleaner onto the surface and wipe with SWIPE Microfiber Kitchen Towel. Oil stains on hobs, wall tiles and floors would be removed. Watch and Jewellery - Pour a small amount (roughly 10ml) of SWIPE Multi-Purpose Cleaner into half a glass of water. Put jewellery items such as watch straps, necklace, bracelets, diamonds, etc., and shake gently for 1-2 minutes. Dirt and stains would be dissolved, leaving your watch and jewelry items looking new! Engine and Car Wheels - Spray SWIPE Multi-Purpose Cleaner onto engines or car wheels, wipe gently and rinse with water. Dirt on engines and brake dust on wheels would be removed. Carpet - Especially good for removing tea, coffee, oil, and bloodstains on carpets and upholstery. Spray onto the surface and allow it to penetrate for 10 seconds. Name: SHIBUI Enzyme Multi Purpose Cleaner, Pet & Baby Safe, Remove Bad Smell Odours Stains, Insect Repellent, Deep Clean 500ML
Description: HIBUI ORGANIC ENZYME MULTI PURPOSE CLEANER is part of SHIBUI new ecological home care range of human & nature family products. All the products are made with natural, biodegradable and non-toxic ingredients. It works the same, if not better than conventional mass market products. ORGANIC ENZYME MULTI PURPOSE CLEANER is an advanced floor cleaner formulation that does not depend on detergent as the main ingredient. Enzyme cleaners contain biological enzymes to break down molecules in dirt, food stain and bad odours. Once the enzymes break the molecules down into smaller pieces, those dirt molecules can be removed effectively. No residuals and bad odours remain after the floor is mopped. The formulation is made from unique proprietary blend of plant-derived ingredients that are all-natural, non-toxic and biodegradable.
